title: Celebrity Gossip Part 1 - Kanye's Parenting Advice
description: Rough weekend for concert goers. Lady Gaga and Post Malone had to cut their shows short for two very different reasons. And Kanye says he has been giving Kim Kardashian plenty of parenting advice to make sure his kids are educated properly.
